data.description:
Nestled in the heart of the historical district, 521 W Green St, Hastings, presents a charming opportunity for those seeking a blend of comfort and heritage. This inviting residence boasts four spacious bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, offering ample space for family living or guest accommodation. The property features a beautifully fenced-in yard, providing a private oasis for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. With its prime location in a distinguished historical area, this home combines the allure of yesteryear with the conveniences of modern living, making it a perfect choice for anyone looking to create lasting memories in a place of their own..
Open House Sunday, April 7th from 1pm-3pm
